=== EVENT_SPACE_WHALE_MIGRATION ===
# id: 66
# title: Space Whale Migration
# chinese_title: 太空鲸鱼迁徙
# category: AlienContact
# mode: starmap

Enormous bio-luminescent creatures drift through space in a great migration. Their gentle calls echo through your hull. They seem to be following ancient stellar currents.

* [[+20 fuel] Follow their path to a fuel-rich region]
  ~ gain_fuel(20)
  跟 (gēn) — follow
* [[Gain radical 鱼] Study their navigation instincts]
  ~ gain_radical("鱼")
  鱼 (yú) — fish
* [[+25 credits] Carefully harvest shed bio-crystals]
  ~ gain_credits(25)
  采 (cǎi) — harvest
* [[Heal 5 HP] Let their calming songs soothe the crew]
  ~ heal_crew(5)
  歌 (gē) — song
* [[+10 hull] Use their magnetic wake to recalibrate systems]
  ~ gain_hull(10)
  磁 (cí) — magnetic
